@baseUrl = http://localhost:5199
@tenantSlug = demo

### ✅ Create staff member (201)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/staff
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant: {{tenantSlug}}

{
  "staffType": "Dentist",
  "firstName": "Alice",
  "lastName": "Smith",
  "email": "alice.smith@demo.com",
  "phone": "+15551234567",
  "hireDate": "2024-01-15",
  "specialty": "General Dentistry",
  "colorHex": "#3B82F6"
}

###

### ✅ Get all staff (200)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/staff
X-Tenant: {{tenantSlug}}

###

### ✅ Get staff by ID — replace {id} after creating
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/staff/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
X-Tenant: {{tenantSlug}}

###

### ❌ Not found (404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/staff/ffffffff-ffff-ffff-ffff-ffffffffffff
X-Tenant: {{tenantSlug}}

###

### ❌ Unauthorized (401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/staff

###

### ❌ Validation error - missing required fields (400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/staff
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant: {{tenantSlug}}

{
  "staffType": "",
  "firstName": "",
  "lastName": ""
}

###

### 🗑️ Delete staff member (204)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/staff/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
X-Tenant: {{tenantSlug}}

